- Add custom attribute to define serialization/validation/api-property groups for each property
 * see vendor/zircote/swagger-php/src/Attributes/Property.php
- Add custom property decider that based on groups you can decide whether
  a property should be exposed or not in:
 * API documentation
    + see vendor/zircote/swagger-php/src/Processors/BuildProperties.php
    + it should ignore or remove the property if the decider return a group that is not included
 * Serialization
    + It should just ignore the property in case the decider return a group that is not included
 * Validation
    + It should just ignore the property validation in case the decider return a group that is not included
